---
title: Homemade Falafel Flatbread with chips and cooling yoghurt sauce
description: Gorgeous golden herby falafels, fresh salad and a creamy cooling tzatziki combine in this multifaceted dish to create the perfect blend of flavours and textures.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R07_W42_IE_IEVV14328-2_Main_high-2d862773.jpg
